name: YA TE VI = "I already saw you”
description:
“This work was made by "Maquita" an artist who sells her drawings in the squares of the city of La Plata, when I saw it I fell in love and decided to buy it. I bought it for 2 usd in Argentinean currency, and asked her permission to take it to HEN. Then I scanned it and retouched it digitally at home.

Just as in HEN artists value and collect other artists, I thought it was nice to take that to the streets, and support local artists, not recognized.”
